<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Security</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">
    <%= link_to 'replicate.info', root_path, class: "text-blue-600 font-semibold" %> is email-first and intentionally simple, following modern security practices without unnecessary complexity.
    To request additional documentation, contact
    <%= mail_to 'support@replicate.info', 'support@replicate.info', class: "text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline transition" %>.
  </p>

  <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2">
    <li><span class="font-semibold">No integrations required.</span> All content is delivered by email. We don't connect to Slack, GitHub, Jira, or other internal systems.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Hosted on Heroku.</span> We run on AWS with encrypted storage and enforce HTTPS for all traffic.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Data is encrypted in transit and at rest.</span> Background jobs run in isolated Heroku worker dynos.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">We collect only essential data.</span> Used solely to deliver insights and generate reports. Never sold, shared, or used to train AI models.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">You own your data.</span> We'll export or delete it upon request.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">No user accounts or persistent logins.</span> Managers receive secure reports by email only.</li>
    <li><span class="font-semibold">Internal tools are protected.</span> Only authorized staff have access to customer data, and only when needed for support.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-6 mb-6">
    <a href="/coaching" class="inline-block rounded-md bg-neutral-700 px-5 py-3 text-white font-semibold shadow hover:bg-neutral-600 transition cursor-pointer">
      Try the Demo →
    </a>
  </p>

  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
    <%= link_to 'Terms of Service', '/terms', class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-1 transition" %> &nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <%= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '/privacy', class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline hover:underline-offset-4 decoration-1 transition" %>
  </p>
</div>
